-- Triggers (25+): updated_at triggers, sync aliases, normalize plate,
--   area occupancy, business rules, payment protect, reservation protect
--
-- Seed Data:
--   4 vehicle_types | 3 floors | 21 areas | 22 area_vehicle_types
--   40 B2 slots | 6 gates | 4 users (admin01/manager01/staff01/driver01)
